# Formatting style for the Kalman filter library.
#
# Based on the LLVM coding style (2-space indent, 80 column limit, pointer
# bound to the type-name side). Pinned with explicit keys so that results are
# reproducible across clang-format versions; CI enforces this with
# clang-format 18.
---
Language: Cpp
BasedOnStyle: LLVM
Standard: c++17
ColumnLimit: 80
IndentWidth: 2
TabWidth: 2
UseTab: Never
PointerAlignment: Right
ReflowComments: true
SortIncludes: CaseInsensitive
